課程教材 Course Material
	    講義。    

參考書目 References
	    1.     J.S. Wu, Analytical and Numerical Methods for Vibration Analyses, John Wiley & Sons Singapore Pte. Ltd.,.2013.
2.     J.S. Przemieniecki, Theory of Matrix Structural Analysis, McGraw-Hill, New York, 1968
3.     K.J. Bathe, Finite Element Procedures in Engineering Analysis, Prentice-Hall, New York, 1982.
4.     L. Meirovitch, Analytical Methods in Vibrations, Macmillan, London, 1967.
5.     W.K. Wilson, Practical Solution of Torsional Vibration Problems, 3rd ed., Vol. 2, Chapman & Hall, London., 1963.
6.     F.H. Todd, Ship Hull Vibration, Edward Arnold Ltd., London, 1961.    

